               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>Lot One has a focus on multi-discipline enhancements, buildings and structures works across the Scotland and LNE Routes. It has.an initial indicative value over the effective life of the Framework of Three Hundred and Twenty Million Pounds (320 000 000,00 GBP). The maximum value of works which may be awarded to the Lot One Supplier is 950 000 000,00 GBP. In exceptional circumstances, including but not limited to, the insolvency of a Framework Supplier or termination of a Framework contract for one of the other lots, NR may award further works (i.e. works with a value beyond 950 000 000,00 GBP) to the Lot One Supplier, provided that the total Framework Value of 1 900 000 000,00 GBP is not exceeded.</P>
